## üß© Requirements

### Python
- **Python 3.12 or newer**

### Dependencies
The following Python packages are required:

```text
cryptography >= 46.0.3
lxml >= 6.0.2
openpyxl >= 3.1.5
orjson >= 3.11.5
pandas >= 2.3.3
```
```bash
pip install cryptography lxml openpyxl orjson pandas
```

